I"Z<blockquote>
  <h2 id="redux">Redux</h2>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li>action : store(저장소)로 data를 보내는 방법</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// actions -&gt; index.js

export const LOGIN = 'LOGIN';
export const LOGOUT = 'LOGOUT';

export const login = () =&gt; {
  return {
    type: LOGIN,
    payload : (생략가능)
  }
}

export const logout = () =&gt; {
  return {
    type: LOGOUT,
    payload : (생략가능)
  }
}
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>Reducers : action을 통해 타입을 정의 했으면, 그 결과로 인해 상태를 어떻게 바꿀 것인지 정의하는 함수</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// reducers -&gt; userReducer.js

import { LOGIN, LOGOUT } from '../actions';

const initalState = {...};

                    // es6 문법, default값 선언
const userReducer = (state = initialState, action ) =&gt; {
  switch(action.type) {
    case LOGIN:
    return {
      ...
    }
    case LOGOUT:
    return {
      ...
    }
    default:
      return state;
  }
}

export default userReducer;
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>store : state를 저장하는 객체</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// store -&gt; store.js

import {createStore} from 'redux';
import userReducer from '../reducers/userReducer';

export const store = createStore(userReducer);
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>Provider : 하위 컴포넌트에게 store에 관련한 모든 것들에 대한 접근을 허용</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// index.js

import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import App from './App';
import store from './store/store';
import { Provider } from 'react-redux';
import * as serviceWorker from './serviceWorker';

ReactDOM.render(
  ⭐️&lt;Provider store={store}&gt;⭐️ // 모든 component를 Provider로 감싸주고 store를 넘겨준다.
    &lt;App /&gt;
  &lt;/Provider&gt;,
  document.getElementById('root')
);
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="react-hooks를-이용한-component와-redux-연결">React hooks를 이용한 Component와 Redux 연결</h4>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux';
import { login, logout } from './actions';

const state = useSelector(state =&gt; state.userReducer);

const dispatch = useDispatch();

dispatch(login(인자&lt;없을 경우 생략&gt;));
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>… 추후 업데이트 예정 …</p>

