  <h2 id="redux-1">Redux</h2>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li>Flux개념을 바탕으로한 State관리 라이브러리</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/72539723/119288900-82237980-bc84-11eb-893e-eb86eb5506a2.png" alt="redux" /></p>

